ConfigurationHolder - Class in be.ac.ulb.infof307.g09.config
This class is meant to be used by: - the tests, in order to instantiate the configuration and Mocks only once - the Main class in order to build the application only once - The getters are used by every class to access the implementation hiding behind the interface The properties files (key - values) are read by Configuration and stored inside it This class use use the configuration file to instanciate each implementations through introspection the implementations of each interface and link them all (in loadConfiguration).
